Detailed Description

This class contains all the common variables that a dynamically created queue will need.

These include the CopyableQueueCVectors (vec) and QoS parameters. The owner module MUST call the clean() function to de-alloc memory from the vectors.

KNOWN BUG: Queue name does not always change... (for the gui)
